<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c3">{أَزِفَتِ الآزِفَةُ *لَيْسَ لَهَا مِنْ دُونِ اللَّهِ كَاشِفَةٌ}</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
